                            <comment id="16812657" author="zsxwing" created="Mon, 8 Apr 2019 17:53:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=sandeep.katta2007&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;sandeep.katta2007&quot;&gt;sandeep.katta2007&lt;/a&gt; I cannot reproduce this locally. Ideally, when we decide to remove an executor, we should remove it from all places rather than counting on a TCP disconnect event which may not happen sometimes. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
